{"tid":2060555,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"提防bitcoin騙案","createTime":"2020-06-11T17:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T17:26:33.000Z","uid":254716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"70d0e82ade1df8e443f806644ecbbba0913b2f25","tid":2060555,"uid":254716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T17:26:33.000Z","msg":"利申唔係讀呢科 只係有睇開新聞<br />\n<br />\n最近單左個app叫heymandi 好似連登開 入面嘅仟奇百趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同tinder一樣 好多假profile 今晚就撞到個salesman<br />\n<br />\n條女揾人買bitcoin，話自己入左八千，賺左少少，想再入；問佢啲friend呢，佢話啲friend唔識呢啲bitcoin嘢，但之後又改口話係啲friend介紹佢去呢間公司 <br />\n<br />\n講左一陣 佢擺條link出嚟話係透過agent賣bitcoin<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WTeQ6fD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWTeQ6fD.png&h=4d545fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n間公司條link係咁：<a href=\"https://rely-intl.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frely-intl.com&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0j%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=63e4636d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rely-intl.com</a><br />\n自稱叫Rely International Limited，你可能會想google吓，發現真係有呢間公司，仲係英國嘢喎堅喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仔細睇睇，網址同入面啲料同真嗰個完全唔同，而且仲冇地址<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rq5djBy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frq5djBy.png&h=ad79ff02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLinkedin得幾個followers，會計師公會仲要未批到佢哋條數，再揾一揾，強國有個網站仲評到佢可靠度得一點幾分，唔係政治不正確，就真係好似有啲嘢喎。最後發現間公司喺印度登記，好地地香港一間國際有限公司，偷人名之後仲要喺印度注冊？？<br />\n<br />\n最後條女走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qa6LU9Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQa6LU9Y.png&h=f1c25e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上騙案真係層出不窮，尤其是bitcoin呢啲要更加小心"}]}